<div id="filmDesc">
	<h2 class="headline subheadline caps">Synopsis</h2>						
	<p>(Sci-Fi, Supernatural, Drama) A 155 year old slave from the Civil War era goes to great lengths in order to avoid pain and slow his aging. He saves the life of an 18-year-old boy from certain death, pulling him into another reality where he was never born and begins teaching him how to survive. Their journey will decide if both will be free to live a self-centered life or to risk their lives to save innocent people from harm.</p>											
